{"tid":891961,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"海傲灣轉招標發售兼增優惠","createTime":"2018-11-06T13:50:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-07T05:01:11.000Z","uid":83582,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"5db4607783be615559c6e2a51bb4f75d860ffa74","tid":891961,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T13:50:21.000Z","msg":"靜雞雞減價 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n11月06日(二) 20:34<br />\n新盤專輯：海傲灣轉招標發售兼增優惠<br />\n<br />\n樓市交投低迷，發展商相繼引入高成數按揭促銷新盤。九龍建業(00034)旗下油塘<br />\n海傲灣，剛更新銷售安排，原正銷售的112伙即日停售，同時發出新銷售安排，以招標形式發售134伙，11月10至30日期間每日下午2時開始招標，下午7時截標。<br />\n<br />\n消息透露，該盤是次新增樓價80%高成數一按，建築期付款計劃的總折扣較之前略增2%，同時一房、兩房單位獲贈家具套餐，明顯發展商希望透過連串優惠加速去貨。<br />\n<br />\n資料顯示，該盤首張價單推出130伙，折實平均呎價19,913元，上月開售至今累沽50伙。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20181106/bkn-20181106203409722-1106_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20181106%2Fbkn-20181106203409722-1106_00842_001.html&d=xly6xkOdUO7KnkCtzsZR7r%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=645261af\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20181106/bkn-20181106203409722-1106_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"432ee6b264203998ec6bf15769a6c0c51a7b626c","tid":891961,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T13:51:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6376825acf7751400855bdbc799ea4af0792c9e0","tid":891961,"uid":103647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T13:59:49.000Z","msg":"招標係咪姐係10000蚊呎都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},{"pid":"17de16380d3c25fe6439b9df81d2012d69533f40","tid":891961,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6376825acf7751400855bdbc799ea4af0792c9e0","tid":891961,"uid":103647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T13:59:49.000Z","msg":"招標係咪姐係10000蚊呎都得<img src=\"/asset